text: Nicola Birkner (2010) Nicola Birkner (born 7 December 1969 in Berlin) is a German sailor. Together with Wibke Bülle she competed at the 2000 Olympics finishing fifth. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Berlin Category:German female sailors (sport) Category:Sailors at the 2000 Summer Olympics – 470 Category:Olympic sailors of Germany
